### PHẦN 15 - TEST HỆ THỐNG HOÀN CHỈNH

### 1. Kiểm tra PolicyService
GET http://localhost:5002/api/policy/test

### 2. Kiểm tra ChatService
GET http://localhost:5003/api/auth/test

### 3. Tạo Policy (Trigger Event Flow)
POST http://localhost:5002/api/policy/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Agent Test User"
}

### 4. Tạo Policy khác
POST http://localhost:5002/api/policy/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Real-time Test Customer"
}

### 5. Test Manual Notification (Backup)
POST http://localhost:5003/api/notification/simulate-policy

###
### 🧪 TEST SEQUENCE:
### 
### STEP 1: Start Services
### - docker run -d --name rabbitmq -p 5672:5672 -p 15672:15672 rabbitmq:3-management
### - cd PolicyService && dotnet run
### - cd ChatService && dotnet run
### 
### STEP 2: Open Client
### - Mở test-client.html trong browser
### - Click "Connect to ChatService"
### - Verify status = Connected ✅
### 
### STEP 3: Test Chat
### - Mở thêm tab browser với test-client.html
### - Test chat giữa các agents
### 
### STEP 4: Test Policy Creation
### - Chạy request #3 và #4 ở trên
### - Hoặc click "Create Test Policy" trong client
### - Verify notification xuất hiện real-time
### 
### STEP 5: Verify End-to-End
### - PolicyService tạo policy ✅
### - Event published to RabbitMQ ✅
### - ChatService receives event ✅
### - SignalR notification sent ✅
### - Client receives notification ✅
###
### 🎯 SUCCESS: Khi tạo policy, tất cả clients nhận notification trong < 1 giây
###